มทฤษฎีอ้างอิงอย่างไร\r\n23. ปรับการเขียนปัจจัย....มีความสัมพันธ์กับ.... อย่างไม่มีนัยสำคัญทางสถิติ (p>0.05) หรือ มีความสัมพันธ์อย่างมีนัยสำคัญ (p<0.05)\r\n24. การอ้างอิงความสอดคล้อง หรือขัดแย้ง ให้ตรวจสอบด้วย และหากไม่ใช่กลุ่มนักศึกษาใช้ปีที่ 4 ก็ไม่ควรนำมาเขียนอภิปราย อาจเขียนในบทนำได้\r\n25. การอ้างอิงในเนื้อหายังไม่ถูกต้อง\r\n26. การอ้างอิงท้ายบทความ อ้างอิงที่ 1 ปี พ.ศ. มี 2 ค่า และอ้งอิงที่ 7 ไม่ใส่ตำแหน่ง และวุฒิการศึกษา\r\n27. คำที่มีสระ ำ เช่น ทำ นำ คำ จะไม่มีสระ  ำ แต่เป็นสระ า\r\n5 ข้อเสนอแนะควรปรับ เป็นเสนอแนะว่างานวิจัยนี้ได้อะไร จะให้ใครเอาไปใช้และใช้อย่างไร รวมทั้งเสนอแนะงานวิจัยที่ต่อเนื่อง 2-3 เรื่อง\r\n(กรุณาแก้ไขทับไฟล์ word ชื่อ \"28 มนัสนันท์ เพชรลูกอนทร์ (ฉบับส่งให้ผู้เขียนแก้ไข)\" เนื่องจากได้ปรับรูปแบบให้ท่านแล้วค่ะ)','O-02-033.doc','O-02-033.doc',0),(174,179,467,NULL,NULL,'O-02-034-1.doc',462,NULL,NULL,'O-02-034-2.',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,2,'กรุณาแก้ไข ทับ ไฟล์ word ที่ส่งให้ในครั้งนี้ได้เลยค่ะ เนื่องจากได้ปรับรูปแบบให้ท่านแล้ว','O-02-034.doc','O-02-034.doc',0),(175,180,468,NULL,NULL,'O-02-035-1.doc',467,NULL,NULL,'O-02-035-2.docx',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,2,'กรุณาแก้ไข ทับ ไฟล์ word ที่ส่งให้ในครั้งนี้ได้เลยค่ะ เนื่องจากได้ปรับรูปแบบให้ท่านแล้ว','O-02-035.doc','O-02-035.doc',0),(176,181,430,NULL,NULL,NULL,335,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,2,'DECISION: ACCEPT WITH MINOR REVISION\r\n\r\n1 Clarity of the topic \r\n-The topic is clear and well- explained.\r\n2 Well-written abstract that includes all salient point of the article\r\n-The abstract includes all important details of the study.\r\n3 Introduction and sections that discusses the details of the article\r\n-The introduction clearly presented the topic and objective of the study.\r\n4 Summary The summary illustrated the salient findings of the study.\r\n5 Use of appropriate citation and references with correct format\r\n-The citation must be revisited for editing.\r\n-The references must include a format (no initial for some entries and use of initial for first name)\r\n-The paper should be edited for grammar.\r\nIMPORTANT: \r\nPlease send your revision to any of these emails: jrc.hcu@gmail.com, hcu.epc@gmail.com not later than 12 June 2019.\r\nThe author should send a file explaining how each of the comments has been addressed. See the attached file.','O-03-068.docx','O-03-068.docx',0),(177,182,430,NULL,NULL,NULL,430,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,2,'1. Clarity of the topic\r\nTopic is clear\r\n2. Abstract\r\nThe author wrote “Based on the quasi-qualitative approach taken, it was produced that the application”. This should be written as …, it was found that… \r\n3. Introduction and sections that discusses the details of the article.\r\n-When the author wrote “In public service, the New Public Service is considered as an effort to criticize the Old Public Administration and New Public Management paradigms which are considered not to have a welfare effect and instead spread injustice in providing services to the public.” and no citation was provided (e.g. books, news reports, etc), the reader is caught in quandary since the author was left looking for the context of the research. References should be provided here.\r\n-This sentence also need references “Some of the problems identified in public service in Indonesia are the low accountability and capacity of public service delivery institutions, and the low level of public participation in supporting the implementation of public services.” Who said this?\r\n-The last sentence of the Introduction should be written as “Based on the state-of-the art public service described earlier, this study aimed to examine the administrative process in public service if the chain of custody is applied and a framework is proposed.”\r\n\r\nObjective:\r\nThis paper aims to identify the administrative process in public service if the chain of custody is applied and proposes a framework for implementation of chain of custody in public service administration.\r\n\r\n“According to Merilee S. Grindle (1980) that the successful implementation of public policy is influenced by two fundamental variables, namely the policy content (content of policy) and the implementation environment (context of implementation) as shown in the picture above.” The author should delete “that” after the year.\r\n\r\nThe author wrote: “1. The variable contents of this policy include: (“ Things are missing here.\r\n\r\nWhile the authors claim that there is check for validity by extension of observation and member checking, but this is not enough. It is the responsibility of the author to rigorously examine data and present the results in a manner understandable to the readers. In the methodology section, Grindle Framework was shown but the in-depth interview questions – which are assumed to shed some light on the lone objective were not shown. The reader is now wondering if the interview questions were appropriate or was there really an interview. This inconsistencies and uncertainties in the methodology were reflected on the results. The results of the research study did not reflect the results of the interview. While there were only 3 participants,  which is quite a low number, the author should make sure that the findings were taken from the interview data and discussed in relation to the theoretical framework of Grindle to propose a framework for the implementation of Chain of Custody on Public Service Administration in Indonesia. These are not shown in the methodology and results.\r\n\r\n4. Conclusion\r\nIn the Conclusion, the author wrote: “From the results of data collection, it was found that basically the governance component had considerable potential to synergize. However, the lack of communication, coordination and initiation between components of governance causes them to carry out their programs partially without thinking about constructive forms of synergy, even though in reality the program targets intersect with one another.” But these were not seen in the findings. There MUST be a lot of direct quotes from the interview data as evidence to these claims.\r\n5. Citations and references\r\nThe following MUST be in the References Section\r\nDunleavy (2005)\r\nDenhardt and Denhardt (2003)\r\nDwipayana et al. (2003)\r\nKurniawan (2005)\r\nHouck et al. (2018)\r\nYasuda et al. (2006)\r\nCosic (2010)\r\nGasova et al. (2017) \r\n\r\nIMPORTANT: \r\n-The name, email, bionote and other information about the author were removed during the double blind review process. Please kindly return them prior to sending the final draft.\r\n-The author should send a file explaining how each of the comments has been addressed. See the attached file.\r\n-The author should send the revision note to any of the following emails:\r\nhcu.epc@gmail.com, jrc.hcu@gmail.com\r\n-The final draft should be uploaded on the website using the author’s username and password NOT LATER THAN JUNE 12, 2019','O-03-069.docx','O-03-069.docx',0),(178,183,430,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,0),(179,184,401,NULL,NULL,'O-02-002-1.docx',374,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,2,'FFFF',NULL,'O-01-026.docx',0),(180,185,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,0),(181,186,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,0),(182,187,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,0),(183,188,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,0),(184,189,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,0),(185,190,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,0),(186,191,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NUL